            <li>
                <p>Create a new source control publishing destination, or select an existing source control publishing destination. <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="General.Online-Only">See <MadCap:xref href="../../../../Flare/Step5-Building-Publishing-Output/Publishing-Destinations/Process/Creating-Destination-File-Source-Control.htm">Creating Destination Files Using Source Control</MadCap:xref>.</MadCap:conditionalText></p>
                <div class="note">
                    <p class="Note-Text" MadCap:autonum="&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #fdc80b;&quot; class=&quot;mcFormatColor&quot;&gt;Note &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;">When creating a new source control destination, be sure to select <span class="Emphasis">Source Control</span> from the <span class="Emphasis">Type</span> drop-down.</p>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li>Assign the publishing destination to the target you want to publish. <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="General.Online-Only">See <MadCap:xref href="../../../../Flare/Step5-Building-Publishing-Output/Publishing-Destinations/Process/Associating-Publishing-Destinations-Targets.htm">Associating Destination Files With Targets</MadCap:xref>.</MadCap:conditionalText></li>
            <li>Build and publish your output. Your output files will be published to the source control location you specified in the destination. <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="General.Online-Only">See <MadCap:xref href="../../../../Flare/Step5-Building-Publishing-Output/Building-Publishing-Output.htm">Step 5: Building and Publishing Output</MadCap:xref>.</MadCap:conditionalText></li>
